    public abstract class TwoFADevicesResource<T extends UserDevicesDao>
extends UserDevicesResource<T>
    Abstract sub-implementation of the UserDevicesResource. A TwoFADevice must have the ability to skip the module, if desired by the user and the configuration of that server allows it.
